00:17:50.410 --> 00:17:51.480
Bu da ne?!

00:17:52.770 --> 00:17:54.530
Yaprakların sesi miydi?

00:17:54.530 --> 00:17:56.010
Hayır, mümkün değil.  

00:17:57.120 --> 00:17:58.550
Neden?!  

00:17:58.810 --> 00:18:01.200
Kaç, Saeko!  

00:18:07.750 --> 00:18:08.960
Saeko!  

00:18:16.450 --> 00:18:17.620
Komuro?  

00:18:22.620 --> 00:18:24.010
Komuro...  

00:18:24.010 --> 00:18:26.780
Bir sebep istiyorsan, söyleyeyim!  

00:18:26.780 --> 00:18:30.930
